Package: scPAISO
Type: Package
Title: scPAISO: identification and quantification of alternative polyadenylation sites in single cell RNA-seq data 
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Yongjie Liu
Maintainer: Yongjie Liu <yongjieliu.2016@gmail.com>
Description: A pipeline that leverages both reads from 3' tag-based scRNA-seq for de novo mapping and quantification of PASs. Enabling both known and novel PAS detection and isoform-level quantification.
